<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Degen Ola — Web3 Growth Operator</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400;500&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;0,900;1,700;1,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --black: #0a0a0a;
  --white: #f0ede6;
  --cream: #c8c4bb;
  --red: #c8392b;
  --gold: #b8a06a;
  --grey: #141414;
  --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{background:var(--black);color:var(--white);font-family:"DM Mono",monospace;overflow-x:hidden;}

/* GRAIN */
body::after{
content:””;
position:fixed;inset:0;
background-image:url(“data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox=‘0 0 256 256’ xmlns=‘http://www.w3.org/2000/svg’%3E%3Cfilter id=‘noise’%3E%3CfeTurbulence type=‘fractalNoise’ baseFrequency=‘0.9’ numOctaves=‘4’ stitchTiles=‘stitch’/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width=‘100%25’ height=‘100%25’ filter=‘url(%23noise)’ opacity=‘1’/%3E%3C/svg%3E”);
opacity:0.025;
pointer-events:none;
z-index:9998;
}

/* LOADER */
#loader{
position:fixed;inset:0;
background:var(–black);
z-index:9999;
display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
flex-direction:column;gap:24px;
transition:opacity 0.6s ease, visibility 0.6s ease;
}
#loader.hidden{opacity:0;visibility:hidden;}
.loader-name{
font-family:“Bebas Neue”,sans-serif;
font-size:clamp(48px,10vw,120px);
letter-spacing:0.08em;
color:var(–white);
overflow:hidden;
}
.loader-name span{
display:inline-block;
animation:loaderUp 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) forwards;
opacity:0;
transform:translateY(100%);
}
.loader-bar{
width:200px;height:1px;
background:var(–border);
position:relative;overflow:hidden;
}
.loader-bar::after{
content:””;
position:absolute;top:0;left:-100%;
width:100%;height:100%;
background:var(–red);
animation:loadBar 1.2s ease forwards;
}
@keyframes loaderUp{to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}
@keyframes loadBar{to{left:0;}}

/* NAV */
nav{
position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:100;
display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;
padding:18px 40px;
background:rgba(10,10,10,0.96);
backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
border-bottom:1px solid var(–border);
transition:padding 0.3s;
}
.nav-logo{font-family:“Bebas Neue”,sans-serif;font-size:20px;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:var(–white);cursor:pointer;}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:32px;list-style:none;align-items:center;}
.nav-links a{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–cream);text-decoration:none;opacity:0.55;transition:opacity 0.2s,color 0.2s;cursor:pointer;}
.nav-links a:hover,.nav-links a.active{opacity:1;color:var(–red);}

/* STATUS BADGE */
.status-badge{
display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
padding:6px 14px;
border:1px solid rgba(200,57,43,0.35);
font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–red);
}
.status-dot{
width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;
background:var(–red);
animation:pulse 2s ease infinite;
}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1);}50%{opacity:0.4;transform:scale(0.7);}}

/* PAGE TRANSITIONS */
.page{display:none;animation:pageIn 0.4s ease forwards;}
.page.active{display:block;}
@keyframes pageIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}

/* HERO */
.hero{min-height:100vh;padding:110px 40px 80px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.hero-bg{
position:absolute;top:50%;left:-20px;
transform:translateY(-50%);
font-family:“Bebas Neue”,sans-serif;
font-size:clamp(100px,18vw,280px);
color:transparent;
-webkit-text-stroke:1px rgba(255,255,255,0.022);
white-space:nowrap;pointer-events:none;user-select:none;z-index:0;
}
.hero-inner{
position:relative;z-index:1;
display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-end;
min-height:calc(100vh - 190px);flex-wrap:wrap;gap:40px;
}
.hero-main{flex:1;min-width:280px;}
.hero-eyebrow{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.3em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–red);margin-bottom:18px;}
.hero-name{
font-family:“Bebas Neue”,sans-serif;
font-size:clamp(56px,10vw,148px);
line-height:0.92;letter-spacing:-0.01em;
}
.hero-name .italic{font-family:“Playfair Display”,serif;font-style:italic;color:var(–red);font-size:0.85em;}
.hero-sub{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:18px;margin-top:28px;max-width:460px;}
.hero-line{width:36px;height:1px;background:var(–gold);margin-top:9px;flex-shrink:0;}
.hero-sub p{font-size:13px;line-height:1.85;color:var(–cream);opacity:0.78;}

/* PFP */
.hero-side{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-end;gap:20px;flex-shrink:0;}
.pfp-wrap{
width:200px;height:240px;position:relative;
border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
overflow:hidden;
}
.pfp-wrap img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center top;display:block;}
.pfp-wrap::after{
content:””;position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;
height:60px;
background:linear-gradient(to top,var(–black),transparent);
z-index:1;
}
.hero-links{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-end;gap:8px;}
.hero-links a{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–cream);text-decoration:none;opacity:0.45;transition:opacity 0.2s,color 0.2s;}
.hero-links a:hover{opacity:1;color:var(–red);}

/* BOOK CALL BTN */
.book-btn{
display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
background:var(–red);
padding:14px 28px;
font-family:“DM Mono”,monospace;
font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;
color:var(–white);text-decoration:none;
transition:background 0.2s,transform 0.2s;
margin-top:8px;
}
.book-btn:hover{background:#a82d22;transform:translateY(-1px);}
.book-btn::before{content:“→”;}

/* TICKER */
.ticker{background:var(–red);padding:12px 0;overflow:hidden;white-space:nowrap;}
.ticker-track{display:inline-flex;animation:ticker 30s linear infinite;}
.ticker-track span{font-family:“Bebas Neue”,sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:var(–white);padding:0 28px;}
.ticker-track .dot{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);padding:0;}
@keyframes ticker{from{transform:translateX(0);}to{transform:translateX(-50%);}}

/* WHAT I BRING */
.bring{padding:100px 40px;border-top:1px solid var(–border);}
.bring-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:2px;margin-top:48px;}
.bring-item{
padding:48px 36px;border:1px solid var(–border);
position:relative;overflow:hidden;
transition:border-color 0.3s;
}
.bring-item:hover{border-color:rgba(200,57,43,0.3);}
.bring-num{
font-family:“Bebas Neue”,sans-serif;font-size:88px;
color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:1px rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
position:absolute;top:0;right:16px;line-height:1;pointer-events:none;
}
.bring-title{
font-family:“Playfair Display”,serif;
font-size:clamp(22px,2.5vw,32px);
font-weight:900;font-style:italic;
color:var(–white);line-height:1.1;
margin-bottom:16px;
}
.bring-desc{font-size:12px;line-height:1.8;color:var(–cream);opacity:0.6;}

/* ABOUT */
.about{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:60px;padding:100px 40px;border-top:1px solid var(–border);}
.section-label{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.35em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–red);margin-bottom:28px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;}
.section-label::before{content:””;width:22px;height:1px;background:var(–red);}
.about-left h2{font-family:“Playfair Display”,serif;font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,54px);font-weight:700;line-height:1.18;}
.about-left h2 em{color:var(–gold);font-style:italic;}
.about-right{display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;gap:18px;}
.about-right p{font-size:13px;line-height:1.9;color:var(–cream);opacity:0.76;}

/* STATS - animated counters */
.stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);border-top:1px solid var(–border);}
.stat{padding:48px 40px;border-right:1px solid var(–border);}
.stat:last-child{border-right:none;}
.stat-num{font-family:“Bebas Neue”,sans-serif;font-size:64px;line-height:1;color:var(–white);margin-bottom:6px;}
.stat-num span.accent{color:var(–red);}
.stat-num .counter{display:inline;}
.stat-label{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–cream);opacity:0.4;}

/* TESTIMONIALS */
.testi{padding:100px 40px;border-top:1px solid var(–border);}
.testi-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:2px;margin-top:48px;}
.testi-card{
padding:44px 40px;border:1px solid var(–border);
position:relative;overflow:hidden;
transition:border-color 0.3s;
}
.testi-card:hover{border-color:rgba(184,160,106,0.3);}
.testi-card::before{
content:”\201C”;
font-family:“Playfair Display”,serif;
font-size:120px;color:var(–red);opacity:0.12;
position:absolute;top:-10px;left:20px;line-height:1;
pointer-events:none;
}
.testi-quote{
font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;color:var(–white);
opacity:0.88;margin-bottom:28px;position:relative;z-index:1;
font-style:italic;
}
.testi-from{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;}
.testi-dot{width:24px;height:1px;background:var(–gold);}
.testi-name{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–gold);opacity:0.7;}
.testi-role{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:var(–cream);opacity:0.4;margin-top:3px;}

/* PAGE HERO */
.page-hero{padding:120px 40px 60px;}
.page-hero h1{font-family:“Bebas Neue”,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(52px,9vw,128px);line-height:0.92;}
.page-hero h1 em{font-family:“Playfair Display”,serif;font-style:italic;color:var(–red);font-size:0.82em;}

/* CARDS */
.cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:2px;padding:0 40px 80px;}
.card{background:var(–grey);padding:36px;border:1px solid var(–border);position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:background 0.25s;}
.card:hover{background:#1a1a1a;}
.card::after{content:””;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:2px;height:0;background:var(–red);transition:height 0.35s;}
.card:hover::after{height:100%;}
.card-head{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:24px;gap:12px;}
.card-id{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;}
.card-id img{width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:7px;object-fit:cover;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);flex-shrink:0;}
.card-name{font-family:“Bebas Neue”,sans-serif;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:0.04em;}
.card-tw{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.14em;color:var(–gold);text-decoration:none;opacity:0.55;display:block;margin-top:3px;transition:opacity 0.2s;}
.card-tw:hover{opacity:1;}
.card-tag{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–red);border:1px solid rgba(200,57,43,0.3);padding:4px 9px;white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0;line-height:1.4;}
.card-body ul{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;}
.card-body li{font-size:12px;line-height:1.72;color:var(–cream);opacity:0.7;padding-left:15px;position:relative;}
.card-body li::before{content:”—”;position:absolute;left:0;color:var(–gold);font-size:10px;top:2px;}
.card-body li strong{color:var(–white);opacity:1;font-weight:500;}

/* CAPABILITIES */
.cap-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:2px;padding:0 40px 80px;}
.cap-card{padding:40px 36px;border:1px solid var(–border);position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:border-color 0.25s;}
.cap-card:hover{border-color:rgba(200,57,43,0.28);}
.cap-num{font-family:“Bebas Neue”,sans-serif;font-size:68px;color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:1px rgba(255,255,255,0.05);position:absolute;top:8px;right:18px;line-height:1;pointer-events:none;}
.cap-title{font-family:“Playfair Display”,serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:var(–white);margin-bottom:16px;line-height:1.2;}
.cap-list{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;}
.cap-list li{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.02em;color:var(–cream);opacity:0.52;padding-left:11px;position:relative;}
.cap-list li::before{content:”·”;position:absolute;left:0;color:var(–red);font-size:14px;line-height:1;top:-1px;}

/* CONTACT */
.contact-hero{padding:120px 40px 60px;}
.contact-hero h1{font-family:“Bebas Neue”,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(52px,10vw,136px);line-height:0.92;}
.contact-hero h1 em{font-family:“Playfair Display”,serif;font-style:italic;color:var(–red);}
.contact-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:2px;padding:0 40px;}
.contact-block{padding:36px;border:1px solid var(–border);}
.contact-block .label{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.3em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–gold);margin-bottom:10px;}
.contact-block a,.contact-block p{font-size:15px;color:var(–white);text-decoration:none;line-height:1.6;transition:color 0.2s;}
.contact-block a:hover{color:var(–red);}
.contact-book{
padding:36px;border:1px solid rgba(200,57,43,0.3);
background:rgba(200,57,43,0.04);
display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;
}
.contact-book .label{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.3em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–red);margin-bottom:12px;}
.contact-book p{font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:var(–cream);opacity:0.7;margin-bottom:20px;}
.contact-bottom{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-end;padding:60px 40px;border-top:1px solid var(–border);margin-top:40px;}
.contact-big{font-family:“Bebas Neue”,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(32px,6vw,84px);color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:1px rgba(255,255,255,0.07);line-height:1;}
.contact-loc p{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–cream);opacity:0.38;line-height:2.2;text-align:right;}
.dl-btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:12px 22px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);font-family:“DM Mono”,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(–white);background:transparent;cursor:pointer;transition:border-color 0.2s,color 0.2s;}
.dl-btn:hover{border-color:var(–red);color:var(–red);}

/* FOOTER */
footer{padding:26px 40px;border-top:1px solid var(–border);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;}
footer p{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.14em;color:var(–cream);opacity:0.28;}

/* REVEAL */
.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(22px);transition:opacity 0.6s ease,transform 0.6s ease;}
.reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}

/* MOBILE */
@media(max-width:768px){
nav{padding:14px 20px;}
.nav-links{gap:14px;}
.nav-links a{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.12em;}
.status-badge{display:none;}
.hero{padding:88px 20px 60px;}
.hero-inner{flex-direction:column-reverse;align-items:flex-start;min-height:auto;gap:28px;}
.hero-side{flex-direction:row;align-items:flex-end;width:100%;justify-content:space-between;}
.pfp-wrap{width:120px;height:150px;}
.hero-links{flex-direction:row;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;}
.bring-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
.about{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:28px;padding:60px 20px;}
.stats{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
.stat{border-right:none;border-bottom:1px solid var(–border);padding:28px 20px;}
.stat:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.testi-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
.testi,.bring{padding:60px 20px;}
.page-hero{padding:88px 20px 40px;}
.cards{grid-template-columns:1fr;padding:0 20px 60px;}
.cap-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;padding:0 20px 60px;}
.contact-hero{padding:88px 20px 40px;}
.contact-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;padding:0 20px;}
.contact-bottom{flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;gap:16px;padding:40px 20px;}
.contact-loc p{text-align:left;}
footer{padding:20px;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;text-align:center;}
}
</style>

</head>
<body>

<!-- LOADER -->

<div id="loader">
  <div class="loader-name">
    <span style="animation-delay:0s">D</span><span style="animation-delay:0.05s">E</span><span style="animation-delay:0.1s">G</span><span style="animation-delay:0.15s">E</span><span style="animation-delay:0.2s">N</span><span style="animation-delay:0.25s">&nbsp;</span><span style="animation-delay:0.3s">O</span><span style="animation-delay:0.35s">L</span><span style="animation-delay:0.4s">A</span>
  </div>
  <div class="loader-bar"></div>
</div>

<nav>

    <li><a onclick="showPage('proof')" id="nav-proof">Proof of Work</a></li>
    <li><a onclick="showPage('capabilities')" id="nav-capabilities">Capabilities</a></li>
    <li><a onclick="showPage('contact')" id="nav-contact">Contact</a></li>
    <li><div class="status-badge"><div class="status-dot"></div>Open to Work</div></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HOME -->

<div id="home" class="page active">
  <section class="hero">

    <div class="hero-inner">

          <div class="hero-line"></div>
          <p>Growth operator, community architect, and deal closer who went from moderating chats to moving markets. Four years deep in Web3.</p>

        <div class="pfp-wrap">
          <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Degen Ola">

    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="ticker">
    <div class="ticker-track">
      <span>Business Development</span><span class="dot">&#x2736;</span><span>KOL Management</span><span class="dot">&#x2736;</span><span>Community Growth</span><span class="dot">&#x2736;</span><span>Token Strategy</span><span class="dot">&#x2736;</span><span>GTM Execution</span><span class="dot">&#x2736;</span><span>Partnerships</span><span class="dot">&#x2736;</span><span>Raid Operations</span><span class="dot">&#x2736;</span><span>Outbound BD</span><span class="dot">&#x2736;</span><span>Business Development</span><span class="dot">&#x2736;</span><span>KOL Management</span><span class="dot">&#x2736;</span><span>Community Growth</span><span class="dot">&#x2736;</span><span>Token Strategy</span><span class="dot">&#x2736;</span><span>GTM Execution</span><span class="dot">&#x2736;</span><span>Partnerships</span><span class="dot">&#x2736;</span><span>Raid Operations</span><span class="dot">&#x2736;</span><span>Outbound BD</span><span class="dot">&#x2736;</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- WHAT I BRING -->

  <section class="bring">
    <div class="section-label">What I Bring</div>
    <div class="bring-grid">
      <div class="bring-item reveal">
        <span class="bring-num">01</span>
        <h3 class="bring-title">I Cold Call.<br>I Close.</h3>
        <p class="bring-desc">35+ leads sourced from scratch. No warm intros, no referrals. Pure outbound. One closed deal with an AI infrastructure protocol. The pipeline never stops.</p>

        <p class="bring-desc">50+ KOLs recruited and managed. Communities scaled from zero to thousands of daily active users. Raid campaigns, meme wars, AMA operations &mdash; I run the whole thing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bring-item reveal">
        <span class="bring-num">03</span>
        <h3 class="bring-title">I Show<br>Receipts.</h3>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT -->

  <section class="about">

<script>
function showPage(id) {
  var pages = document.querySelectorAll('.page');
  for (var i = 0; i < pages.length; i++) pages[i].classList.remove('active');
  var navs = document.querySelectorAll('.nav-links a');
  for (var i = 0; i < navs.length; i++) navs[i].classList.remove('active');
  document.getElementById(id).classList.add('active');
  var nav = document.getElementById('nav-' + id);
  if (nav) nav.classList.add('active');
  window.scrollTo(0, 0);
  setTimeout(function() { initReveal(id); }, 60);
}

function initReveal(pageId) {
  var page = document.getElementById(pageId || 'home');
  if (!page) return;
  var els = page.querySelectorAll('.reveal');
  var obs = new IntersectionObserver(function(entries) {
    entries.forEach(function(entry, idx) {
      if (entry.isIntersecting) {
        (function(el, d) {
          setTimeout(function() {
            el.classList.add('in');
            // trigger counter if present
            var counter = el.querySelector('.counter');
            if (counter) animateCounter(counter);
          }, d);
        })(entry.target, idx * 70);
        obs.unobserve(entry.target);
      }
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.08 });
  for (var i = 0; i < els.length; i++) {
    els[i].classList.remove('in');
    obs.observe(els[i]);
  }
}

function animateCounter(el) {
  var target = parseInt(el.getAttribute('data-target'));
  var duration = 1200;
  var start = null;
  function step(ts) {
    if (!start) start = ts;
    var progress = Math.min((ts - start) / duration, 1);
    var ease = 1 - Math.pow(1 - progress, 3);
    el.textContent = Math.floor(ease * target);
    if (progress < 1) requestAnimationFrame(step);
    else el.textContent = target;
  }
  requestAnimationFrame(step);
}

window.addEventListener('load', function() {
  setTimeout(function() {
    var loader = document.getElementById('loader');
    if (loader) loader.classList.add('hidden');
    initReveal('home');
  }, 1600);
});
